ygData.messageBody:
I am really sorry to do this to an organized
club. But I can't get the word out. I am starting a new
EverQuest club. I am urgently looking for members. There
will be scheduled events regularly. And guides and
tips. I am also looking for some co-founders. The url
is <a href=http://clubs.yahoo.com/clubs/thealtimateeqlounge target=new>http://clubs.yahoo.com/clubs/thealtimateeqlounge</a>
thank you much for reading. I do not expect many to
join and do NOT entend on hurting this club, but this
was my only option, Jammr10
